    "content": "Changes to the Employer Health Tax or any other premium imposed for purposes similar to the Medical Service Plan premium are excluded and will not be required to be used to increase other employee benefits. If the Employer Health Tax is eliminated and not replaced with another form of Employer paid benefits, Article 23.8 will be triggered.",
